A panhandler takes a vicious beating from a man in a horrifying video uploaded online.

The film, which has more than 3,500 views, shows tree surgeon Joseph Johnson get out of a car and repeatedly punch and kick the man in a sustained attack.

Another man in the background can be heard cheering as the 40-second beating, which took place in Memphis, Tennessee, goes on.

But Mr Johnson says the man is not homeless, once worked for him and stole seven chainsaws from his family business.

